node.text:
Yes, she’s the world’s top-ranked female tennis player, but @NaomiOsaka won us over for her qualities *off* the court. 💖 Soft-spoken yet powerful and always authentic, she brought those same qualities to our new collaboration. The Levi’s® x Naomi Osaka collection, crafted from upcycled denim, takes Levi’s® icons to an unexpected place, celebrating Naomi’s rich heritage with a bold femininity and a sporty attitude—and a bit of her famous dry wit. Plus, you know, crystals and lace-ups. Link in bio.

🎥: @yongwkim 
.

WHERE YOU CAN SHOP THE COLLAB:

Levi’s App (US, UK, France)
Levi.com (Japan)
Levi’s Stores (Harajuku, Osaka, Shanghai, Hong Kong)

node.title: JUST IN: Levi’s® x Naomi Osaka

node.text:
This Juneteenth we wrap on our Beauty of Becoming series with the woman who created and directed the short films, Oge Egbuonu. Through telling stories that celebrate the people that society often casts aside, while embracing the unfolding chapters of her own, Oge Egbuonu is becoming. 

Created and Directed by @ogetheyogi
Music by @phantogram

[Video: Oge is sitting in front of a brown background and green leaves with pink and red floral arrangements. She is wearing a black denim shirt with her name embroidered above the front left breast pocket and black denim jeans. Shots of her walking around in a flower labyrinth of various colors and sitting at a wooden desk on a wooden writing on a piece of paper are shown throughout the video.]

Through breaking down barriers, making history, and pioneering for other LGBTQI+ models and actresses, @leynabloom is becoming. 

Created and Directed by @ogetheyogi
Music by @phantogram

[Video: Leyna is sitting in front of a brown background and green leaves with pink and red floral arrangements. She is wearing a denim jumpsuit with her name embroidered above the front left breast pocket and tied together with a black leather belt. Shots of her walking around in a flower labyrinth of various colors and sitting at a wooden desk on a wooden writing on a piece of paper are shown throughout the video.]

node.text:
Through stepping into the spotlight, prioritizing her own dreams, and making a career shift to acting, @angiebeyince is becoming.

Created and Directed by @ogetheyogi
Music by @phantogram

***
[Video: Angie is sitting in front of a brown background behind a gold frame with pastel colored florals. She is wearing a light blue button up shirt, jeans and bright blue heels. Shots of her walking around in a flower labyrinth of various colors and sitting at a wooden desk on a wooden writing on a piece of paper are shown throughout the video.]

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Levi's on September 02, 2021 tagging @newbalance. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: Levi’s® x New Balance®: Look out for our take on the 990v3, coming soon. Tap the link in bio to download the Levi’s® App and turn on notifications to find out when they’re available—because they won’t last long.

The Tailor Profile Series is back for Volume 3! Meet Orlando based Tailor, Teighlor, who gives us the scoop on what it is like being a denim artist. Link in bio to ready her Q&A.

📸: @joshvillatoro23

THE PERFECT SUMMER SHORT. CUSTOM FOR YOU.
Head to Reels to see how @_viluong customized her shorts at a Levi’s® Tailor Shop. Bring your favorite pair of Levi’s® or find a new favorite in-store and our expert Tailors will crop your perfect short. 

*As long as you’re a Red Tab™ member (US Only), it’s on us, cause we want you to love what you wear and wear it longer.
